diagram.documentation: <html> <head> <style> p {padding:0px; margin:0px;} </style> </head> <body> The Actor-Stakeholder Traceability Matrix provides a comprehensive mapping of the 29 identified actors to their corresponding stakeholder groups within the Advanced Orbital Manufacturing System (AOMS) project. This matrix serves as a crucial tool for understanding the relationships and interactions between the various roles involved in the system's operation and the broader stakeholder categories they represent. By visually linking actors such as the Data Analyst, Business Manager, and Space Station Crew to their respective stakeholder groups, the matrix offers insights into the distribution of responsibilities and interests across the project. This traceability helps in identifying potential communication channels, aligning objectives, and ensuring that all stakeholder needs are adequately addressed through the various actor roles.</body> </html>
